{"tid":1795097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波音 CEO Dennis Muilenburg 因 737 Max 風波辭職","createTime":"2019-12-23T15:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T05:49:26.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47c8aa0a8aadd298b4d8b807f9fc6036090d5583","tid":1795097,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdimse%2F5845cadfecd996e0372f%2Fd005ddc43345919d5171ea29d5dbc486ec4b6f65%%3D&h=636b7d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在波音 737 Max 事故引發的風波持續數月之後，CEO Dennis Muilenburg 今天正式確認將辭去自己擔任的職務。現任董事會主席 David Calhoun 將會在明年 1 月 13 日接任，在那之前，則會由公司現在的 CFO Greg Smith 暫代 CEO 一職。<br />\n<br />\n「為了修復波音與監管機構、客戶以及所有股東的關係，讓人對波音重拾信心，董事會認為這一領導層的變動非常有必要。」在對外發佈的聲明中波音這麼寫道，「波音未來將會重新以保證徹底的透明度為目標，力求和 FAA、全球其它監管方以及客戶達成有效、積極的溝通。」<br />\n<br />\n在 CEO 下台之前，波音剛剛宣佈將會暫停 737 Max 客機的生產。不知在高層換人之後，這款飛機未來的命運會去往什麼樣的方向呢...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2019-12-23-boeing-ceo-dennis-muilenburg-resigns.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fchinese-2019-12-23-boeing-ceo-dennis-muilenburg-resigns.html&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlplHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=5c75ba6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2019-12-23-boeing-ceo-dennis-muilenburg-resigns.html</a>"},{"pid":"591781f1ba825851d795bc0c67f5d18f392b20f1","tid":1795097,"uid":156990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"又係你波音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚癲"},{"pid":"2fa559ed4af5ea072b5b6dbaae8fe020a75f39a1","tid":1795097,"uid":263667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9A56ESg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9A56ESg.jpg&h=95129fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}